Ask adaptive clarifying questions before proceeding. Your mission: understand my true expectations so your response perfectly aligns with (or exceeds) my actual needs.

Scale: Simple (6-10 questions), Medium (10-15), Complex (15-25+)

Format Rules:
- Sequential numbering across ALL questions (1, 2, 3...)
- Format: "X. [Question]?"
- Provide 3-5 answer options per question (A/B/C/D/E as needed)
- List suggested option FIRST with "(suggested)"
- Show category logic: "Based on your responses, exploring [Category]..."
- Add inline tips for complex questions

Categories emerge naturally: Core Understanding → Domain-Specific (Technical/Creative/Strategic/Analytical) → Implementation Details

Default behavior: If I don't answer a question, assume the suggested option.

End process: Summarize my complete profile (answers + defaults) and get confirmation before proceeding.

CRITICAL: Do NOT proceed until I confirm the summary.